snippet.title: 10 Fragrances That Smell Like Christmas | Amazing Spicy, Amber and Gourmand Fragrances
snippet.description:
Hello everyone!

With a Holiday spirit, I want to share with you 10 fragrances that smell like Christmas. These are some of the best spicy, ambery and gourmand fragrances.

Fragrances mentioned:
- Andy Tauer Sundowner
- Baruti Perverso
- Frederic Malle Musc Ravageur
- Serge Lutens Fille En Aiguilles
- Parfum d'Empire Ambre Russe
- Guerlain Shalimar EDP
- Xerjoff Starlight
- Frapin 1270
- Tom Ford Noir Extreme
- Burberry London For Men


Hope you enjoy!
